#. [message]: speaker=Kaleh
#: data/campaigns/Under_the_Burning_Suns/scenarios/01_The_Morning_After.cfg:203
#: data/campaigns/Under_the_Burning_Suns/scenarios_old/01_The_Morning_After.cfg:205
