#: data/campaigns/Under_the_Burning_Suns/scenarios/05_A_Subterranean_Struggle.cfg:2481
#: data/campaigns/Under_the_Burning_Suns/scenarios_old/05_A_Subterranean_Struggle.cfg:2480
