#: data/campaigns/Under_the_Burning_Suns/scenarios/08_Out_of_the_Frying_Pan.cfg:2808
#: data/campaigns/Under_the_Burning_Suns/scenarios_old/08_Out_of_the_Frying_Pan.cfg:2806
